{
  "stem": "8234.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I can't survive with that thing anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I've got to do something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Next day, we stood for appel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so happened I was late, and I was one from the last.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I noticed a broom in the corner.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When we started walking out towards the gate, I walked away and grabbed the broom.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I didn't turn around or nothing-- and started sweeping.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Sweep, sweep, sweep, sweep, sweep, sweep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Sweep to the left, sweep to the right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they locked the gates.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I was with my broom.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I swept.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I swept.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I swept.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What's now?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I cleaned up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I went to a-- to a shed, and I see some whitewash powder.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mixed it up in a bucket, and I painted the gutters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of a sudden I hear, hey, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a German officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He called me and he says, you know behind my barrack is a lot of dirt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] Go and clean it up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I've got another place for you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I created a job for myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I cleaned up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He liked me because I cleaned good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm a good cleaner if I want to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, if I go back to the barracks tomorrow, maybe I won't have that chance.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there was a barrack of the people who worked administration.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The cooks, the kapos-- they had their own barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I went to the German officer-- because he's supposed to tell you where to sweep again-- I seen his name was Grunstad.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went to the barrack and there was a German kapo, a criminal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "With a green triangle.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kapo, whatever.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
